headline.main: King Zulu, Beloved White Bengal Tiger at Audubon Zoo, Dies
headline.print_headline: King Zulu, Beloved White Bengal Tiger at Audubon Zoo, Dies

lead_paragraph: King Zulu, the white Bengal tiger that mesmerized scores of visitors to the Audubon Zoo in New Orleans, has died.
